  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983070/extras/ed24d54b1e7e6590f45bea7f6fd5b615.avif?t=1768834117\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br>MouseVentures is a puzzle game where you control Pipo, a stuffed mouse. He will enter two storybooks to help the characters inside while use magnetism and light to solve the puzzles that stand in their way.<br><br>A little girl's handcrafted plush comes to life due to her imagination. He gets absorbed into storybooks where something isn't quite right and gets tasked with helping the little prince Arthur get his sword and an energetic bunny rescue his friend Quetzacóatl.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983070/extras/a40fc13b180859695c853dd6bb194d1f.avif?t=1768834117\" width=600 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore a book based world</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983070/extras/afcea6662d34a6afe2b608cad3e8618d.poster.avif?t=1768834117\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983070/extras/afcea6662d34a6afe2b608cad3e8618d.webm?t=1768834117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983070/extras/afcea6662d34a6afe2b608cad3e8618d.mp4?t=1768834117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Solve incredible puzzles</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983070/extras/9683d2692f9cd7455f6c4ed84e430499.poster.avif?t=1768834117\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983070/extras/9683d2692f9cd7455f6c4ed84e430499.webm?t=1768834117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983070/extras/9683d2692f9cd7455f6c4ed84e430499.mp4?t=1768834117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Meet amazing characters!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983070/extras/a173cd3b44823f20166cea529be31651.poster.avif?t=1768834117\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983070/extras/a173cd3b44823f20166cea529be31651.webm?t=1768834117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983070/extras/a173cd3b44823f20166cea529be31651.mp4?t=1768834117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983070/extras/a0314dc9cb71f37107ea1d9189626940.avif?t=1768834117\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br>This game was developed as a 4th-year student project at DigiPen Europe-Bilbao for educational purposes. Please check out our publisher page for more information.",
